定的休息日 看情况都是亲戚也没法定 4 我不想接手的原因就是 我对机械也不咋熟 况且制造业每天都在下滑，招人越来越难，也没学机械自动化了都，我要是干倒闭了多愧疚啊。整个厂就靠外协和那 3 台磨齿机 磨齿机是台湾的设备 3 台加起来当时买的得小 500w 我不接手这床子又可惜了。我真的很别扭。而且订单越来越难，人也招不到。我看知乎像我这情况的还不少，在 80 90 年代吃制造业红利的这一代仅仅 20 年就没多少人愿意干机加工了。。希望有朋友给我个回答，我真不知道咋办了。这就是我家农村制造业现状，现在我爸有钱挣 一年真不少 但是明明这么多我居然看不到未来了。 这个实在太他么难了 。求解答！！！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4b3ac447c8ddd5ae990b34fc4042e6fd_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "23 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/450893153"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxrDWp5G7qek7EAMaCDYyNDc3NTkxIOrD54IGMEA4zxlAKnIJNDUwODkzMTUzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1622779289.109448", "card_id": "Q_403043689", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 141}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么中世纪的时候，很多贵族和领主喜欢打猎，打猎有什么趣味？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "又热又累，一身汗，还有一定危险性，他们为什么喜欢打猎？甚至有的地区不许平民进入，专门给他们打猎？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9c3e85928ba0fc0c02744692b05a11d5.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "21 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/403043689"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxrDWp5G7qek7EAMaCDUxODQzNTY2IKzMxvcFMBQ4jANAK3IJNDAzMDQzNjg5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1622779289.1099129", "card_id": "Q_463000516", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《一人之下》529（561）话？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-2ee94f37269cde59b46094cfb5e7e8c0_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "15 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/463000516"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxrDWp5G7qek7EAMaCDY1MTY4NjAyIJ6l44UGMAE4jAFALHIJNDYzMDAwNTE2eACqA